title: Fastboot flashing unlock is not allowed for pixel 3a XL
content:
Hello guys!
My phone pixel 3a XL couldn't unlock device,is say:
D:\fastboot-win(your file)>fastboot flashing unlock
                                                   FAILED (remote: 'flashing unlock is not allowed')
fastboot: error: Command failed

OEM unlock is failed,too:
D:\fastboot-win(your file)>fastboot oem unlock
                                                   FAILED (remote: 'Invalid oem command unlock')
fastboot: error: Command failed

So need back to google survice fixed it,or send to google corporation mail,get unlock.bin file?
